      <scopecontent id="aspace_db53eb553c973df6122e0e6e01cc4551">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The microfilmed records consist of undergraduate and graduate student records, class letters, biographical data on alumni, correspondence, transcripts, and necrology files documenting the students from the Classes of 1902-1991, Yale School of Forestry and Environmental Studies.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
